Usage: deleteIoFiller [-help] [-cell {name list}] [-from <float>]
                      [-prefix <prefix>] [-ring <num>]
                      [-side <top|bottom|left|right>] [-to <float>] [-logic  [ -deriveConnectivity ]]

-help                             # Prints out the command usage
-cell {name list}                 # name list of IO filler cell
                                  # (list, optional)
-deriveConnectivity               # delete connectivity for io Filler
                                  # (bool, optional)
-from <float>                     # delete cell starting from this location
                                  # (float, optional)
-logic                            # delete NON-physical IO Filler created by
                                  # addIoFiller (bool, optional)
-prefix <prefix>                  # prefix of instance names (string, optional)
-ring <num>                       # ring number in multiple io ring design
                                  # (int, optional)
-side <top|bottom|left|right>     # specify cells on which side of design
                                  # (string, optional)
-to <float>                       # delete cell to this location
                                  # (float, optional)